  × Provide screen reader accessible content when using heading elements.
  
    1 │ <!-- Empty heading -->
  > 2 │ <h1></h1>
      │ ^^^^^^^^^
    3 │ 
    4 │ <!-- Whitespace-only heading -->
  
  i All headings on a page should have content that is accessible to screen readers.
  

